  follows that `f‚ÇÅ = f‚ÇÇ` [BGR, Proposition 3.1.5/1][bosch-guntzer-remmert]. -/
theorem eq_of_powMul_faithful (f‚ÇÅ : AlgebraNorm R S) (hf‚ÇÅ_pm : IsPowMul f‚ÇÅ) (f‚ÇÇ : AlgebraNorm R S)
